Biography</st>
<p>

Olson joined the Army from <village wordnetid="108672738" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../822/134822.xml">
Toronto, South Dakota</link></village>
, and by October 13, 1943 was serving as a <rank wordnetid="114429985" confidence="0.8">
<rank wordnetid="108431942" confidence="0.8">
<arrangement wordnetid="107938773" confidence="0.8">
<military_rank wordnetid="114431471" confidence="0.8">
