</arrangement>
</rank>
</rank>
 in the <military_unit wordnetid="108198398" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../843/365843.xml">
15th Infantry Regiment</link></military_unit>
, <military_unit wordnetid="108198398" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../288/165288.xml">
3rd Infantry Division</link></military_unit>
. On that day and the following two weeks, he showed conspicuous leadership during the push across the <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../610/390610.xml">
Volturno River</link> in <system wordnetid="108435388" confidence="0.8">
<economy wordnetid="108366753" confidence="0.8">
