<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../867/11867.xml">
German</link></country>
 forces, personally capturing several enemy positions, until he was mortally wounded during a <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../911/146911.xml">
reconnaissance</link> patrol. He was posthumously awarded the Medal of Honor ten months later, on August 31, 1944.</p>
